---
title: Roasted Zucchini and Tomato Rigatoni with Olives and Plant-Based Mozzarella
description: Tastes of the Mediterranean flavour this roasted veggie pasta. Plump olives and plant-based mozzarella add rich savoury notes to each bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1032_W30_CA_RV161333-1_Mainlow-fe800696.jpg
